alerts.title: Green Warning For Wind In Belgium - Coastal Zone
Orange Warning For Wind In Belgium - Coastal Zone
alerts.description: There is a very strong wind expected with wind gusts between 101 and 130 km/h (91 and 120 km/h with leafed trees). Be careful and follow the instructions of the responsible authority.

alerts.title: Yellow Warning For Storm Surge In Belgium - Coastal Zone
alerts.description: High tides are expected: TAW 5,60 to 6,20 m in Ostend or TAW 6,60 to 7,20 m in Antwerp. Be careful.

alerts.title: Yellow Warning For Wind In Belgium - Coastal Zone
alerts.description: There is a strong wind expected with wind gusts between 80 and 100 km/h (70 and 90 km/h with leafed trees). Be careful.
